snippet.title: Johnny Depp Is Apparently Partying In Europe Amid Amber Heard Abuse Claims
snippet.description: The rocky divorce battle between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard has shown no signs of letting up, as newly-revealed text messages allegedly show abuse dating back to 2014. Meanwhile, Depp has been photographed in Europe apparently partying hard. The Daily Mail has obtained photographs of Depp from Wednesday night in Denmark getting into a scuffle with his own bodyguard after a night of boozing with his band, The Hollywood Vampires, and fans. #InsideEdition
